vity and prevent fraud."},"488":{"id":"/docs/ui/fraud/digital-footprint-16","page_id":"/docs/ui/fraud/digital-footprint","type":"text","url":"/docs/ui/fraud/digital-footprint#analyzing-software-hardware-environment-and-screen-data","content":"Verify the authenticity of devices and detect potential tampering or manipulation by analyzing the software, hardware, and screen data of each user device."},"489":{"id":"/docs/ui/fraud/digital-footprint-17","page_id":"/docs/ui/fraud/digital-footprint","type":"text","url":"/docs/ui/fraud/digital-footprint#behavioral--environmental-analysis","content":"Monitor user behavior in real-time and flag deviations that could indicate fraudulent or automated activities."},"490":{"id":"/docs/ui/fraud/digital-footprint-18","page_id":"/docs/ui/fraud/digital-footprint","type":"text","url":"/docs/ui/fraud/digital-footprint#geofencing-for-location-based-regulation-compliance-igaming","content":"Integrate with real-time location tracking to validate that transactions align with local regulations, ensuring compliance while blocking suspicious attempts to manipulate location data."},"491":{"id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud","page_id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud","type":"page","content":"Getting Started","url":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud"},"492":{"id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud-0","page_id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud","type":"text","url":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud","content":"Ambriel is a comprehensive suite of fraud prevention and compliance solutions."},"493":{"id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud-1","page_id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud","type":"heading","url":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud#what-can-you-do-with-ambriel","content":"What can you do with Ambriel?"},"494":{"id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud-2","page_id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud","type":"heading","url":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud#how-can-you-use-ambriel","content":"How can you use Ambriel?"},"495":{"id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud-3","page_id":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud","type":"heading","url":"/docs/ui/fraud/fraud#fraud-prevention","content":"Fraud Prevention"},"496":